{"tid":2317360,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"（社福界入）想問關於助理活動幹事一職","createTime":"2020-12-08T13:29:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-13T17:53:05.000Z","uid":60947,"like":1,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"4f59cf1dd31416bc1ea70d5b4a4689b5e287447a","tid":2317360,"uid":60947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T13:29:05.000Z","msg":"是甘的 <br />\n最近見到有份工寫住 助理活動幹事 <br />\n做青少/兒童嘅<br />\n上班地點應該我屋企樓下行8分鐘就到<br />\n工作內容同職責都係照顧小朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都適合自己 <br />\n<br />\n但我有社科top up degree，一年TA經驗，<br />\n搵開約萬三一個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上年報個MSW唔收，今年同之後都會繼續報<br />\n自知自己無社福同搞活動經驗<br />\n但目標係想做兒童中心/學校社工 <br />\n<br />\n身邊有朋友叫我話應該搵一級/二級活動幹事 <br />\n但份工工作內容、工作地點對我嚟講又真係好吸引<br />\n如果我開價一樣萬三得唔得呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n助理活動幹事title係差啲但其實重唔重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我未apply既 <br />\n想考慮清楚先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求各位巴絲賜教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：對社福界一無所知的人"},{"pid":"0e8c2f5e00739c8acd62a56f086e4f8b5a6f5a36","tid":2317360,"uid":276658,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T14:07:10.000Z","msg":"似打雜，但如果你真係可以堅持等msw offer，呢個工作經驗對你都有用。<br />\n<br />\n加油"},{"pid":"31e7ab0bef72e80b146e9769d460b9fdeecb1865","tid":2317360,"uid":353267,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T14:09:56.000Z","msg":"其實係咪有咗工作經驗<br />\nGpa 就已經唔重要<br />\n報msw"},{"pid":"7d499b54f56ee50791eb3ce4b960073544bfb668","tid":2317360,"uid":213217,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T15:05:47.000Z","msg":"有個fd degree 唔過3, 做一年社福低層，拎推薦去cu 讀社工轉科master.  雖然唔知係咪個個有。"},{"pid":"cb2df8a14ddb86e292616e97a75325d21aed6efd","tid":2317360,"uid":60947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quo